tionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615207\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104plk1665702651617.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/plk1665702651617.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/plk1665702651617.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"plk1665702651617\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Rate at which the value of the spin button is incremented, expressed as a percentage. Default is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">5</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"plk1665702651617__topic_d101510e1_d101511e1_d101512e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"plk1665702651617__p_d101513e1_d101514e1_d101515e1\">\n            \n                                 Accel\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Percentage</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"plk1665702651617__section_dzx_k42_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1172877e67\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"plk1665702651617__table_d11951e1_d11952e1_d11953e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Repeat</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Increment\n                  Value</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"plk1665702651617__section_uqm_m42_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1172877e118\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"plk1665702651617__p_d101522e1_d101523e1_d101524e1\">To disable acceleration, specify zero (0).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"plk1665702651617__p_d101525e1_d101526e1_d101527e1\">Every time the repeat interval defined by the\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Repeat</span> property elapses, it is shortened by the percentage\n        specified until the maximum repeat rate (about 20 repetitions per second) is reached.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"plk1665702651617__p_d101528e1_d101529e1_d101530e1\">After that, every time the repeat interval elapses,\n        the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Increment Value</span> is incremented by the percentage specified.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"plk1665702651617__section_a5k_442_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1172877e138\">Applies To</h2><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vad1665703094620.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Repeat</a><p>Repeat interval for auto-repeat behavior, in milliseconds. The default is 250 (four repetitions per second).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vyv1665702651765.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Increment Value</a><p>Amount by which the value in the spin button is increased each time it is clicked. The default is 1.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615207\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615207\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Acceleration (Accel) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Rate at which the value of the spin button is incremented, expressed as a percentage. Default is 5 . Accel = Percentage Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Repeat and Increment Value Description To disable acceleration, specify zero (0). Every time the repeat interval defined by the Repeat property elapses, it is shortened by the percentage specified until the maximum repeat rate (about 20 repetitions per second) is reached. After that, every time the repeat interval elapses, the Increment Value is incremented by the percentage specified. Applies To uspinbutton (SpinButton) Related Links Repeat Repeat interval for auto-repeat behavior, in milliseconds. The default is 250 (four repetitions per second). Increment Value Amount by which the value in the spin button is increased each time it is clicked. The default is 1. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}